9. Letter No. of Deputy Conservator of Forests (Budget, Planning and Development), Maharashtra State, Nagpur:
The Proposal: -
Setting up of Special Tiger Protection Force (STPF) for Tadoba-Andhari Tiger Reserve and Pench Tiger Reserve
The 224 temporary posts created under the scheme have been notified in the year 2024-25 with reference numbers 6 and 7.
Government approval has been granted to continue from date 01.03.2024 to date 28.02.2025 under the Government Decision.
2. Now under the letter of Reference No.9, Deputy Conservator of Forests (Budget, Planning and Development), Maharashtra
The State of Nagpur has constituted a Special Tiger Protection Force (STPF) for Tadoba-Andhari Tiger Reserve and Pench Tiger Reserve.
A proposal has been submitted to the government for approval to continue till 01.03.2025 and 28.02.2026.
3. Temporary posts included in the structure of administrative divisions as well as those created after prior review approval but not included in the structure.

Tadoba-Andhari Tiger Reserve and Pench Tiger Reserve vide Government Decision of Finance Department, Reference No.8
